== IPMC Learning Path

The Incubator PMC (IPMC) oversees podlings and mentors.  
This path provides background and exercises for effective participation.

== Steps

1. **Read:** link:https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/INCUBATOR/Incubator+PMC+Onboarding[Incubator PMC Onboarding]  
2. **Slide deck** link:https://training.apache.org/presentations/apache/incubator/IPMC/index.html[IPMC Onboarding]  
3. **Quiz:** link:https://canvas.instructure.com/enroll/N33MBP[IPMC Onboarding Quiz]  
4. **Practice:** link:https://canvas.instructure.com/enroll/C8994Y[IPMC Scenarios Training]

